1
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:07,872
SAM: We're going to stall, Owais. We need to level out.

2
00:00:07,872 --> 00:00:11,520
OWAIS: Hold on to your seat, Sam. We're going to make this plane fly.

3
00:00:11,520 --> 00:00:14,808
L: What's going on? Why are we shaking so much?

4
00:00:14,808 --> 00:00:21,000
ARAESA: Everyone, please fasten your seatbelts. We're experiencing some turbulence.

5
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:23,952
OWAIS: We're coming out of the dive. Hold on to your seats.

6
00:00:23,952 --> 00:00:26,472
L: This is crazy! What's happening?

7
00:00:26,472 --> 00:00:31,608
ARAESA: Everyone, please remain calm. This is just turbulence.

8
00:00:31,608 --> 00:00:34,176
OWAIS: We're going to make it through this. Just hold on.

9
00:00:34,176 --> 00:00:38,722
SAM: Owais, I think we're crashing. We need to do something.

10
00:00:38,722 --> 00:00:44,170
ARAESA: Everyone, please stay calm. We're experiencing a minor storm.

11
00:00:44,170 --> 00:00:46,810
L: This is insane! We're going to die!

12
00:00:46,810 --> 00:00:49,786
OWAIS: We're not going to crash. We're going to make it through this.

13
00:00:49,786 --> 00:00:51,932
SAM: What... what just happened?

14
00:00:51,932 --> 00:00:54,908
OWAIS: We made it through the storm. We're going to land safely.

15
00:00:54,908 --> 00:01:00,164
ARAESA: Everyone, please prepare for landing. We're starting our descent.

16
00:01:00,164 --> 00:01:02,492
L: I... I think I'm going to be sick.
